53:09.311 --> 53:12.147
["Give Yourself a Try"
by The 1975 continues playing]

53:23.867 --> 53:24.784
Hey, Mom.

53:26.995 --> 53:28.205
Would you like to dance?

53:30.415 --> 53:31.791
I would love to dance.

53:45.972 --> 53:46.890
Thank you.

53:48.308 --> 53:50.185
Oh, shit. Act innocent.

53:51.811 --> 53:53.396
You two looked great out there.

53:54.022 --> 53:55.732
Um... thank you, sir.

53:56.233 --> 53:57.943
Yeah, never would've happened in my day.

53:58.985 --> 53:59.945
Two prom kings.

54:00.820 --> 54:03.406
It wouldn't have happened.
Something to see.

54:04.282 --> 54:07.494
Yeah, it was, uh...
unexpected to us too.

54:07.577 --> 54:08.411
Hmm.

54:08.662 --> 54:09.788
There you are.

54:09.871 --> 54:13.833
Guys, this is my husband Josh.
That's Charlie St. George, Alex Standall.

54:13.917 --> 54:15.460
Well, congratulations.

54:16.378 --> 54:18.171
-Thank you.
-Hi.

54:18.255 --> 54:20.799
-[Josh chuckles]
-All right, enjoy the evening, you two.

54:21.800 --> 54:22.634
Be good.

54:28.723 --> 54:30.016
Foundry's gay?

54:30.767 --> 54:32.560
Mind's blown.

54:32.644 --> 54:36.523
["True Feeling" by Galantis plays]
♪ Feel you through and through ♪

54:36.606 --> 54:38.525
♪ Ooh ooh-ooh ooh ♪

54:38.608 --> 54:40.360
♪ Ooh ooh-ooh ooh ♪

54:42.445 --> 54:46.116
♪ It might get hard
When you're growing older ♪

54:46.199 --> 54:50.078
♪ But I'll be here
And I'll be your shoulder ♪

54:50.161 --> 54:53.039
♪ I can see it now ♪

54:53.999 --> 54:56.835
♪ I can see it now... ♪

54:56.918 --> 55:01.381
[Clay] As the night got later,
we just kept dancing and dancing

55:02.299 --> 55:03.842
like there was nothing else.

55:05.218 --> 55:06.928
Like it was the end of the world.

55:08.138 --> 55:10.223
[tense music plays]

55:14.728 --> 55:16.771
Like it was the end of the world.

55:32.078 --> 55:33.204
Somebody help!

55:33.621 --> 55:35.123
Somebody help, please!

55:35.206 --> 55:36.916
[students call for help]

55:39.377 --> 55:40.378
Back up!

55:41.588 --> 55:43.590
[mournful music plays]

55:47.635 --> 55:48.720
[Clay] And it was.

55:51.848 --> 55:53.850
[ominous tone resonates]

55:56.353 --> 55:58.271
[music stops]

56:03.610 --> 56:07.572
[Alex reads text]

58:03.897 --> 58:05.690
[man] Well done, Ed. Well done.
